=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我諗緊千與千尋個湯婆婆係咪都會剋死亡筆記，因為佢可以隨意幫人改名，連本人都唔會記得自己原名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你哋又諗到邊個？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n角都五個心臟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdda1e4e63bda6917207c1705d5a809982039c5a","tid":237451,"uid":88479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T12:19:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果寫角都但唔寫死因，咁佢應該係會五個心臟同一時間麻痹而死，定係要寫佢五次先死？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n角都啲心唔係屬於自己計唔計"},{"pid":"181d7f4d511625759fd7486578e538870685573b","tid":237451,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T12:30:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果寫角都但唔寫死因，咁佢應該係會五個心臟同一時間麻痹而死，定係要寫佢五次先死？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n角都啲心唔係屬於自己計唔計</blockquote><br />\n呢層又係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔通要逐個搵返佢哋個名再寫先有效？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算用死神之眼都淨係睇到角都個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f23097eaa7fec7c9b02f62a0fb0bb8d9671c37c","tid":237451,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T12:30:08.000Z","msg":"艾爾"},{"pid":"13d70303d6f4f2c51c67d0652dae751bcab7b4e6","tid":237451,"uid":112784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T12:33:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>艾爾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n破壞鍊成陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15047141ba46c9598e87e53341f2ed035af4ebd1","tid":237451,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T12:34:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>邊個話一定要心臟麻痺死？</blockquote><br />\n又係嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但叮噹可以點死？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n死亡筆記剩係殺到人類</blockquote><br />\n咁呢個post已經可以完</blockquote><br />\n控制大雄殺叮噹算唔算</blockquote><br />\n好似講過話如果死因牽涉到另外一個人，就會單純變心臟麻痺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁如果我分兩條寫<br />\nA在XXX處被人殺死<br />\nB在XXX處殺人之後回家自殺<br />\n<br />\n咁又成唔成功?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n日劇版死筆夜神月試過喺同一個地方，寫A因為保護男友而畀槍殺死，而B就係拎槍向A男友開槍之後，用同一把槍畏罪自殺(B本身職業關係有槍)<br />\n最後A，B都死晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b9ee921cabeb1c7331542c09e6cbc103552d265","tid":237451,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T12:43:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>艾爾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n破壞鍊成陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗鋼鍊入面殺唔死嘅，本身應該得賀恩漢，但佢最後自己選擇去死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c6ac4b0503ce2a7ca7ba6c4b8c5e93e72085ff9","tid":237451,"uid":86692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T12:46:40.000Z","msg":"卡卡西、冇人見過佢真樣"},{"pid":"e66fd2932ddb609a48d6db2d84b3e26ef5a5e248","tid":237451,"uid":51917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T12:48:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dd5580a1927573a220980098d73a049851194623","tid":237451,"uid":30085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T12:50:11.000Z","msg":"卡兹"},{"pid":"d944731cc1d0f1b5c4678ab094091561554ce655","tid":237451,"uid":30673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T12:52:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://farm9.staticflickr.com/8618/15914620337_1f2eaf5ca6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm9.staticflickr.com%2F8618%2F15914620337_1f2eaf5ca6.jpg&h=61e2dc74&s={SIZE}